      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in wonderful shape! It\u2019s been super dependable for me, runs like a dream, and has plenty of life left in it for its next adventure. It\u2019s clean, well-maintained, and ready to hit the road today. I\u2019d love for it to go to a great new home\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
