    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically sound example of the iconic S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six breathes through individual throttle bodies and is mated to a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Extensive preventative maintenance has been performed, including a VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural integrity and variable valve timing are within spec. The suspension geometry remains precise, complemented by a factory limited-slip differential for predictable power delivery out of corners. Presented in solid driver condition with honest wear consistent with its age, this M3 offers the raw, analog feedback that modern performance cars lack. A well-maintained enthusiast spec ready for the street or track.",
      "price": 34500.0,
