    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a well-preserved example of comfort and reliability, perfect for a driver who values a turn-key experience. The exterior paint retains a deep, reflective luster, and while you may find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper from standard highway travel, the body remains straight and free of any significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin has been kept in impressive shape; the leather upholstery is supple and free of cracks or odors, reflecting a smoke-free ownership history. All interior electronics, including the navigation system and heated seats, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and an engine that idles quietly. It has been serviced regularly, with a recent oil change and a brand-new set of performance all-season tires just installed. The brakes feel firm, and the suspension provides a composed, rattle-free ride. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next chapter.",
